ment","type":"text","url":"/docs/development#启动开发环境","content":"Git"},"124":{"id":"/docs/development-21","page_id":"/docs/development","type":"text","url":"/docs/development#启动后端","content":"首先，你需要克隆本仓库到你的本地（你可能需要 fork 一份到你的仓库中，并且使用 --depth=1 来加速克隆）："},"125":{"id":"/docs/development-22","page_id":"/docs/development","type":"text","url":"/docs/development#启动后端","content":"然后，你需要安装依赖，我们使用了 PNPM 作为包管理器，并不建议你使用其他的管理器安装。"},"126":{"id":"/docs/development-23","page_id":"/docs/development","type":"text","url":"/docs/development#启动后端","content":"在您提交相关 PR 时，我们也会检查您是否使用了 PNPM，如果没有，我们将会拒绝您的 PR（一个项目多个 lock 总不是一个好的选择）。"},"127":{"id":"/docs/development-24","page_id":"/docs/development","type":"text","url":"/docs/development#启动后端","content":"接下来，我们就可以开始启动后端的开发环境了。"},"128":{"id":"/docs/document","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"page","content":"文档撰写","url":"/docs/document"},"129":{"id":"/docs/document-0","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document","content":"Mix Space 的文档撰写规范"},"130":{"id":"/docs/document-1","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"heading","url":"/docs/document#一些规范","content":"一些规范"},"131":{"id":"/docs/document-2","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"heading","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"一些问题"},"132":{"id":"/docs/document-3","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document","content":"我们随时欢迎你对 Mix Space 的文档做出贡献，但撰写文档是一件不易之事，我们更加希望你能规范贡献内容，减少我们的工作量。"},"133":{"id":"/docs/document-4","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document","content":"部分内容来自于 https://github.com/mx-space/docs-archived/pull/163"},"134":{"id":"/docs/document-5","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document","content":"在撰写本文档之前，请确保你有基础的 Markdown 知识，并了解 Markdown 的语法，如果你不够了解，请使用 Typora 等 Markdown 编辑器进行撰写。"},"135":{"id":"/docs/document-6","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document","content":"我们在目前 Mix Space 的 V3 文档中，使用的文档框架是 FumaDocs，它的文档地址是：https://fumadocs.vercel.app/"},"136":{"id":"/docs/document-7","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document","content":"请在撰写之前详细阅读它，并且在你设备本地完成撰写之后，在本地运行开发服务器进行工作情况检查，确保它符合你的预期，减少你 Pull Request 之后我们的检查工作量。"},"137":{"id":"/docs/document-8","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些规范","content":"撰写 Git Commit Message 时，请尽可能遵守 Git Commit Message 的规范，具体可在网络查询，如果你不了解，可以在本仓库使用 pnpm commit 命令在修改完成后引导生成它。"},"138":{"id":"/docs/document-9","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些规范","content":"中英文之间请使用空格隔开，这基本上是撰写中英文混合文本时大家所认同的基本规范。"},"139":{"id":"/docs/document-10","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"为什么要写这么全面呢？甚至教别人改动源码。"},"140":{"id":"/docs/document-11","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"这是极不正确的文档写法。"},"141":{"id":"/docs/document-12","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"别人会写的自然会写，不会写的教他，他会不知道这个地方到底要不要搞、怎么搞、是不是有另外一种方法。"},"142":{"id":"/docs/document-13","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"更多的选择只会影响新手的判断，让他们不知道到底该怎么做。"},"143":{"id":"/docs/document-14","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"偏偏就是出现改动源码的地方就是有多种选择："},"144":{"id":"/docs/document-15","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"你可以在文件后方传入值，比如 node index.js --arg1=value1"},"145":{"id":"/docs/document-16","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"你可以改动源码，在 xxx/xxx.ts 第 xxx 行到 xxx 行，修改对应的配置。"},"146":{"id":"/docs/document-17","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"你甚至可以写一个插件，在插件中进行配置。"},"147":{"id":"/docs/document-18","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"你这样让用户怎么选择？文档部署应该只选择最容易让人读明白的部署方式，这种改动源码的提一嘴在哪个文件就是了，为什么要写具体行数 & 告诉别人怎么改呢？"},"148":{"id":"/docs/document-19","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"如果碰到了一个 object，用户改漏了一个逗号，那这个问题的责任谁来承担呢？文档编写者吗？开发者吗？用户吗？"},"149":{"id":"/docs/document-20","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"很明显都不是，也很明显都要承担责任。不要让局面陷入到如此困境中 😕"},"150":{"id":"/docs/document-21","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"如果你有魔改方面的内容，可以提交到对应区域的社区部署教程内。"},"151":{"id":"/docs/document-22","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"这些面板程序随时都有可能会发生变化，我们无法保证文档的时效性。"},"152":{"id":"/docs/document-23","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"我们也不建议这样写任何官方类文档，因为会使得你的文档结构更加复杂，并且难以维护。"},"153":{"id":"/docs/document-24","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"本质上服务器面板部署方式的核心还是那几种方式。"},"154":{"id":"/docs/document-25","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"如果你有相关内容，可以提交到对应区域的社区部署教程内。"},"155":{"id":"/docs/document-26","page_id":"/docs/document","type":"text","url":"/docs/document#一些问题","content":"我们希望文档的结构能够更加简洁易用，这样对开发者，对用户都有好处。"},"156":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"page","content":"进阶部署","url":"/docs/core/advanced"},"157":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced-0","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/advanced","content":"通过源码部署 Mix-Space 后端"},"158":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced-1","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core/advanced#要求","content":"要求"},"159":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced-2","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core/advanced#克隆并安装","content":"克隆并安装"},"160":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced-3","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core/advanced#构建--bundle","content":"构建 & Bundle"},"161":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced-4","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core/advanced#配置-ecosystemconfigjs","content":"配置 ecosystem.config.js"},"162":{"id":"/docs/core/advanced-5","page_id":"/docs/core/advanced","type":"h