","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#日记","content":"标记「回顾日记」，并自动将其归档到「回顾日记」页面"},"325":{"id":"/docs/core/features-10","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#日记","content":"私人日记密码保护，只有知道密码的人才能查看"},"326":{"id":"/docs/core/features-11","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#日记","content":"定时发布，可以将日记定时发布到未来的某个时间点"},"327":{"id":"/docs/core/features-12","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#评论","content":"评论是一个网站的重要组成部分，Mix Space 的评论功能非常强大，它支持："},"328":{"id":"/docs/core/features-13","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#评论","content":"反垃圾评论，使用 Mix Space 的反垃圾评论系统配合多种自定义规则，可以有效的防止垃圾评论"},"329":{"id":"/docs/core/features-14","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#评论","content":"邮件通知，当有人评论时，会发送邮件通知给文章作者"},"330":{"id":"/docs/core/features-15","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#xlog-集成","content":"通过 Mix Space 的 xLog 功能，你可以将你的博客文章同步到 xLog 平台。并且当你没有为文章写摘要的时候，可以直接使用 xLog 平台生成的摘要，当然你也可以使用自己的 GPT API Key 去调用 GPT 生成文章摘要。"},"331":{"id":"/docs/core/features-16","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#xlog-集成","content":"xLog 是面向所有人的最棒的链上、开源的博客社区。"},"332":{"id":"/docs/core/features-17","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#文件管理","content":"你可以使用 Mix Space 上传文件，然后在任意地方中使用，比如文章中，或者是日记中。你可以使用 Markdown 语法插入图片，也可以使用 HTML 语法插入图片。"},"333":{"id":"/docs/core/features-18","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#通知","content":"Mix Space 支持多种通知方式，让你不错过任何一条重要的通知。"},"334":{"id":"/docs/core/features-19","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#通知","content":"邮件通知，当有人评论时，会发送邮件通知给文章作者"},"335":{"id":"/docs/core/features-20","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#通知","content":"Bark 通知支持"},"336":{"id":"/docs/core/features-21","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#友链","content":"Mix Space 的友链系统支持自助申请，你可以在后台设置是否需要审核，如果需要审核，你可以在后台设置通过 OR 拒绝理由。并且在后台可以看到友链的可用性检查结果。"},"337":{"id":"/docs/core/features-22","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"Mix Space 有着强大的计划任务功能，它们都被统一管理，你可以在后台执行计划任务："},"338":{"id":"/docs/core/features-23","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"备份数据库"},"339":{"id":"/docs/core/features-24","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"清除缓存、访问记录、临时文件"},"340":{"id":"/docs/core/features-25","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"推送百度搜索"},"341":{"id":"/docs/core/features-26","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"推送 Algolia 搜索"},"342":{"id":"/docs/core/features-27","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"删除过期的数据"},"343":{"id":"/docs/core/features-28","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#计划任务","content":"etc..."},"344":{"id":"/docs/core/features-29","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#其他","content":"Mix Space 还有很多其他功能，比如："},"345":{"id":"/docs/core/features-30","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#其他","content":"动态化配置前端，你可以在后台设置前端的配置，比如网站名称，网站描述，网站图标等等"},"346":{"id":"/docs/core/features-31","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#其他","content":"云函数，你可以在后台设置云函数，让你的网站更加强大"},"347":{"id":"/docs/core/features-32","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#其他","content":"Algolia Search，你可以在后台设置 Algolia Search，让你的网站支持站内搜索功能"},"348":{"id":"/docs/core/features-33","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#其他","content":"项目展示功能，你可以向访客展示你的项目，展现你的技术能力"},"349":{"id":"/docs/core/features-34","page_id":"/docs/core/features","type":"text","url":"/docs/core/features#其他","content":"迁移，Mix Space 支持从 Markdown 导入文章，也支持导出文章为 Markdown。"},"350":{"id":"/docs/core","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"page","content":"引言","url":"/docs/core"},"351":{"id":"/docs/core-0","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core#快速开始","content":"快速开始"},"352":{"id":"/docs/core-1","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core#一些你需要知道的事情","content":"一些你需要知道的事情"},"353":{"id":"/docs/core-2","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core#遇到报错怎么办","content":"遇到报错怎么办？"},"354":{"id":"/docs/core-3","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"heading","url":"/docs/core#mix-space-的组成结构","content":"Mix Space 的组成结构"},"355":{"id":"/docs/core-4","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core","content":"在本章节，我们将完成的是 后端 的安装，而 前端 的安装则需要你阅读 前端主题文档。"},"356":{"id":"/docs/core-5","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core","content":"Mix Space 是一个一款简洁而不简单的个人博客系统，它够快，够现代。你可以利用它构建一个属于自己的个人空间，记录生活，分享知识。"},"357":{"id":"/docs/core-6","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core","content":"Linux / macOS"},"358":{"id":"/docs/core-7","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core","content":"Linux 内核版本 >= 4.19"},"359":{"id":"/docs/core-8","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core","content":"Memory >= 1G"},"360":{"id":"/docs/core-9","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#快速开始","content":"我们提供了两种部署方式，社区贡献了一种自动脚本模式，同时社区用户也分享了更多的部署方式，你可以根据自己的喜好选择一种部署方式。"},"361":{"id":"/docs/core-10","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#快速开始","content":"还有更多部署方式吗？欢迎您向文档提交 Pull Request 以分享您的部署方式。按上方后端部署文档完成你的部署后，你可以通过下面的方式继续部署 Mix Space 前端 （为什么分开部署？请查看 一些你需要知道的事情）"},"362":{"id":"/docs/core-11","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#遇到报错怎么办","content":"新时代新风气，我们遇到了一个人工智能蓬勃发展的时代，所以在你遇到了问题的时候请先询问 各种 Ai 助手程序，它们会帮助你解决大部分疑问。"},"363":{"id":"/docs/core-12","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#遇到报错怎么办","content":"如果你遇到了一些人工智能解决不了的问题，那么请再次阅读文档，如果文档依旧没有解决你的问题，那么请在对应仓库的 GitHub Issues 中提出你的问题，我们会尽快解决。"},"364":{"id":"/docs/core-13","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#mix-space-的组成结构","content":"所以，Mix Space 由两部分组成：后端 和 前端。如果你没法理解的话，请先询问 各种 Ai 助手程序关于前后端分离博客程序的定义，比如ChatGPT、Claude、Gemini、Kimi 等等，以此来了解它们、以及知道它们的区别。"},"365":{"id":"/docs/core-14","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#mix-space-的组成结构","content":"总之你需要知道的便是：这不是像 Typecho、WordPress 这样的「一步曲」就搞定的系统，而是需要 「两步曲」 才能完成安装。"},"366":{"id":"/docs/core-15","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#mix-space-的组成结构","content":"但万幸的是，我们开发者已经为你准备好了一切，你只需要按照文档推荐的步骤来操作即可，即使你不是开发者，也可以轻松完成安装。"},"367":{"id":"/docs/core-16","page_id":"/docs/core","type":"text","url":"/docs/core#mix-space-的组成结构","content":"知道了这些，你就可以避免掉大部分的问题了，开始安装体验吧！"},"368":{"id":"/docs/themes/community","page_id":"/docs/themes/community","type":"page","content":"社区分享","url":"/docs/themes/community"},"369":{"id":"/docs/themes/community-0","page_id":"/docs/themes/community","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/community","content":"社区用户分享的部署方式"},"370":{"id":"/docs/themes/community-1","page_id":"/docs/themes/community","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/community","content":"你可以参考他们的部署方式，但我们不保证它们的可用性。如果你也有教程想要与大家分享的话，欢迎您向文档提交 Pull Request 以分享您的部署方式。"},"371":{"id":"/docs/themes","page_id":"/docs/themes","type":"page","content":"前端主题列表","url":"/docs/themes"},"372":{"id":"/docs/themes-0","page_id":"/docs/themes","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes","content":"基于 Mix Space 后端 API 开发的前端主题列表"},"373":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"page","content":"Kami 主题","url":"/docs/themes/kami"},"374":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-0","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami","content":"一个简洁、优雅、现代的博客主题"},"375":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-1","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/kami#现状","content":"现状"},"376":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-2","page_id":"/do