问题，请在 Kami 仓库提交 issue 并详细描述问题。"},"390":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-16","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#检查内核版本","content":"如果你的内核版本小于 4.19，请升级内核。或者使用最新的 Ubuntu / Debian。"},"391":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-17","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#配置-env","content":"复制 .env.example 为 .env"},"392":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-18","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#配置-env","content":"编辑 .env 文件，它看起来应该是这个样子的"},"393":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-19","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#更新指南","content":"根据是否对 Kami 进行过修改，可以选择以下两种更新方式："},"394":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-20","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#标准更新","content":"适用于未修改源代码的用户。"},"395":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-21","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#标准更新","content":"即使未进行源码修改，也可能遇到代码合并冲突。此时建议参考下方的手动更新方法。"},"396":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-22","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#手动更新","content":"适用于修改过源码的用户。"},"397":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-23","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#手动更新","content":"将 kami 文件夹改为任意名字，例如修改为 kami.d，然后拉取 kami 前端仓库，更新到稳定版本："},"398":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-24","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#手动更新","content":"然后将更新前之前配置时修改过的文件，如在 kami.d 中的 .env 和 public 文件夹复制到 kami，将你的修改的部分依次修改替换完成。"},"399":{"id":"/docs/themes/kami-25","page_id":"/docs/themes/kami","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/kami#手动更新","content":"安装依赖、构建、启动前端："},"400":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"page","content":"Yun 主题","url":"/docs/themes/yun"},"401":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-0","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/yun","content":"A light & fast & lovely mx web style."},"402":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-1","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/yun#安装步骤","content":"安装步骤"},"403":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-2","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/yun#克隆项目","content":"克隆项目"},"404":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-3","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/yun#安装依赖","content":"安装依赖"},"405":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-4","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/yun#配置服务","content":"配置服务"},"406":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-5","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/yun#开始构建","content":"开始构建"},"407":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-6","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/yun#启动前端","content":"启动前端"},"408":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-7","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/yun","content":"由于 Yun 主题将不再维护，此文档将不再更新，但是你仍然可以使用它。"},"409":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-8","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/yun#配置服务","content":"如果你部署 Mix Space 后端与部署 Yun 前端在同一台服务器，并且后端监听的端口为 2333，那么你可以跳过这一步。"},"410":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-9","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/yun#配置服务","content":"前往 ./server/constant.ts"},"411":{"id":"/docs/themes/yun-10","page_id":"/docs/themes/yun","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/yun#配置服务","content":"修改为你的后端 API 地址。"},"412":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"page","content":"备份与回滚","url":"/docs/usage/backup"},"413":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup","content":"在 Mix Space 中内有备份功能，并且每日默认自动备份，数据无价请定期手动下载备份包。"},"414":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/backup#备份","content":"备份"},"415":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/backup#自动备份","content":"自动备份"},"416":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"回滚"},"417":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#备份","content":"在后端中 其他 - 备份 中点击立即备份，即备份到绝对目录："},"418":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#备份","content":"~/mx-space/core/data/mx-space/backup/20xx-xx-xx_xx:xx:xx/backup-20xx-xx-xx_xx:xx:xx.zip"},"419":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#自动备份","content":"目前该功能仅支持备份到支持 S3 协议的云服务，暂不支持其他类型的云服务。当然，你也可以通过设置计划任务等方法达到和此功能一样的效果。"},"420":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#自动备份","content":"设置入口：设定 - 系统 - 备份，填入云服务所提供的对应参数即可。"},"421":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"该操作涉及修改数据库，请多备份几个工作日的 backup，数据无价请谨慎操作！"},"422":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"一般情况下回滚只会导致 analyze 数据页丢失 IP & PV 的数据。"},"423":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"Linux 和 macOS 可直接上传备份包，并且无需修改包名一致即可回滚，以下操作仅针对使用 Windows 用户访问后端回滚的情况。"},"424":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"在后端中 其他 - 备份 中点击立即备份，将之前在电脑里的 backup.zip 上传到刚刚生成的备份目录里进行重命名替换。"},"425":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-12","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"例：假如刚刚生成的备份是 backup-2022-09-01_23:33:33.zip 将想进行回滚的备份包 backup-2022-01-14_05:14:19.zip 修改为刚刚生成的备份一样的名字："},"426":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-13","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"不要在 Windows 下重命名，Windows 不支持将英文冒号作为文件名的一部分"},"427":{"id":"/docs/usage/backup-14","page_id":"/docs/usage/backup","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/backup#回滚","content":"替换完成会提示“数据库有变动，将在 x 秒后重载页面”，重载先检查文章评论等有没有丢失。"},"428":{"id":"/docs/usage","page_id":"/docs/usage","type":"page","content":"使用指南","url":"/docs/usage"},"429":{"id":"/docs/usage-0","page_id":"/docs/usage","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage","content":"探索 MixSpace 的使用方式"},"430":{"id":"/docs/usage-1","page_id":"/docs/usage","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage#官方指南","content":"官方指南"},"431":{"id":"/docs/usage-2","page_id":"/docs/usage","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage","content":"本章节将会带您了解 Mix Space 的一些功能，以及如何使用它们。"},"432":{"id":"/docs/usage-3","page_id":"/docs/usage","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage","content":"温馨提示：此指南需要一定的基础知识 & 理解能力，请准备好哦～"},"433":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"page","content":"OAuth 2.0","url":"/docs/usage/oauth"},"434":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth","content":"使用 OAuth 2.0 登录 MixSpace"},"435":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#如何配置","content":"如何配置"},"436":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"新建应用"},"437":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#后台设置","content":"后台设置"},"438":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#和主人身份绑定","content":"和主人身份绑定"},"439":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth","content":"在 Core v7.0.0 版本，Mx-Space 重写了第三方登录功能，抛弃了 Clerk，转而直接使用对应的账户授权 SDK 实现第三方登录。"},"440":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"参考以下两篇："},"441":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"在 GitHub 新建 OAuth 应用"},"442":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"在 Google Cloud Console 新建 OAuth 应用"},"443":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"对于 GitHub，Homepage URL 填写前端地址，Authorization callback URL 根据后台提示复制粘贴。"},"444":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"对于 Google，你可能需要先配置好 OAuth 权限请求页面，其中已获授权的网域填写根域名，API 范围选择非敏感范围的三项。OAuth 应用中 已获授权的 JavaScript 来源 填写前端地址，已获授权的重定向 URI 根据后台提示复制粘贴。"},"445":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#新建应用","content":"完成后会获取 Client ID 和 Client Secret，将他们复制下来备用。"},"446":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-12","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#后台设置","content":"进入博客后台 -> 设定 -> 登录方式，在 OAuth 部分对应的平台名称下填写对应的 Client ID 和 Client Secret，保存后测试是否可以调用授权，若可调用即可启用并保存。"},"447":{"id":"/docs/usage/oauth-13","page_id":"/docs/usage/oauth","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/oauth#和主人身份绑定","content":"在测试时通过 OAuth 授权登录后会提示是否将此账号设置为主人，允许即可。"},"448":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"page","content":"Obsidian 插件","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian"},"449":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian","content":"使用 Obsidian 插件发布内容到 Mix Space"},"450":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#介绍","content":"介绍"},"451":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"功能特性"},"452":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#安装与使用","content":"安装与使用"},"453":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#介绍","content":"Obsidian Mix Space Plugin 是一个 Obsidian 插件，可以将 Obsidian 笔记直接发布到 Mix Space。"},"454":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"发布/更新内容到 Mix Space（支持 Note 和 Post）"},"455":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"自动识别内容类型"},"456":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"反向链接转换（[[Obsidian 链接]] → Mix Space URL）"},"457":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"Frontmatter 自动补全"},"458":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"多环境配置（Profile）"},"459":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#功能特性","content":"AI 生成标题和 slug"},"460":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#安装与使用","content":"详细的安装步骤和使用说明请参考 GitHub 仓库："},"461":{"id":"/docs/usage/obsidian-12","page_id":"/docs/usage/obsidian","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/obsidian#安装与使用","content":"https://github.com/mx-space/obsidian-mixspace-plugin"},"462":{"id":"/docs/usage/search","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"page","content":"Algolia Search","url":"/docs/usage/search"},"463":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search","content":"使用 Algolia 搜索"},"464":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/search#介绍","content":"介绍"},"465":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/search#使用","content":"使用"},"466":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/search#新建应用","content":"新建应用"},"467":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/search#创建索引index","content":"创建索引（Index）"},"468":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/search#获取相关变量","content":"获取相关变量"},"469":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/search#后台配置","content":"后台配置"},"470":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#介绍","content":"Algolia 是一个数据库实时搜索服务，能够提供毫秒级的数据库搜索服务，并且其服务能以 API 的形式方便地布局到网页、客户端、APP 等多种场景。"},"471":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#介绍","content":"像 VuePress 官方文档就是使用的 Algolia 搜索，使用 Algolia 搜索最大的好处就是方便，它会自动爬取网站的页面内容并构建索引，你只用申请一个 Algolia 服务，在网站上添加一些代码，就可以实现一个全文搜索功能。"},"472":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#使用","content":"在这之前，你需要先在 Algolia 官网注册一个账号，或者直接用第三方登录。"},"473":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#新建应用","content":"登录 Algolia 账号，进入控制台，在左上角点击 Applications 下列表，点击 New Application，填写应用名称，选择 BUILD 订阅（免费），选择好数据中心，点击 Create Application，即可创建一个应用。"},"474":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#新建应用","content":"一些额外说明的地方都在图片上标注了，可参考下面的图片。"},"475":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-12","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#创建索引index","content":"在新建应用之后，你会直接跳转到如下图所示的界面，只需要在输入框中输入一个索引名称，点击 Create Index，即可创建一个索引。"},"476":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-13","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#创建索引index","content":"请记住你所创建的索引名称（Index Name），后面的步骤会用到。"},"477":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-14","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#获取相关变量","content":"接下来，在左下角找到齿轮图标，进入设置，在右侧找到 API Keys，进入，这里有两个变量需要复制下来备用，分别是 Application ID 和 Admin API Key，请复制下这两个变量的值，后面的步骤会用到。"},"478":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-15","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#后台配置","content":"进入后台，设定->系统->Algolia Search，将“开启 Algolia Search”开关打开，将前面准备的 IndexName、Application ID（AppID） 和 Admin API Key（ApiKey） 填入对应的框中，右上角保存即可。"},"479":{"id":"/docs/usage/search-16","page_id":"/docs/usage/search","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/search#后台配置","content":"至此，Algolia 搜索的配置就完成了。稍等一会，就可以尝试在主页用 Ctrl + K 调用 Algolia* 进行站内搜索了。*"},"480":{"id":"/docs/usage/security","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"page","content":"Key 加密与安全性","url":"/docs/usage/security"},"481":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security","content":"加密你的 MixSpace"},"482":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"如何开启"},"483":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/security#自动化加密配置进阶指令非必要","content":"自动化加密配置（进阶指令）（非必要）"},"484":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/security#疑难解答","content":"疑难解答"},"485":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security","content":"在 v3.41.0 后续版本，加入了敏感 Key 加密功能。默认为关。"},"486":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security","content":"为什么需要 Key 加密。"},"487":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security","content":"假设黑客通过某种手段数据库被脱库。如果开启了 Key 加密，即便是拿到了全部数据也不能解密某些关键数据，例如配置项中的各类 API Key。"},"488":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security","content":"但是，也需要谨慎开启此功能，开启后你需要记住加密秘钥。否则，你也将会永远丢失这些数据。"},"489":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"你可以附加 --encrypt_enable 来启动服务。如："},"490":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"可以通过附加 --encrypt_key <key> 来指定加密密钥，长度必须为 64 位，且只有小写字母和数字。请牢记此密钥。或者通过环境变量 MX_ENCRYPT_KEY 也可以指定密钥。"},"491":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"若开启加密，则需注意密钥长度必须为 64 位且只有小写字母和数字，不然会在初始化时报错。注意这是不可逆的，务必保存自己的秘钥。\nAPI Key."},"492":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"密钥可以通过 openssl rand -hex 32 命令生成。请务必牢记。"},"493":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-12","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"MX_ENCRYPT_KEY --encrypt_key 不是必须的，默认取机器的\nmachine-id。"},"494":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-13","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#如何开启","content":"此操作是不可逆的，操作前请备份数据库。"},"495":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-14","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#自动化加密配置进阶指令非必要","content":"此操作是不可逆的，操作前请备份数据库。"},"496":{"id":"/docs/usage/security-15","page_id":"/docs/usage/security","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/security#疑难解答","content":"如果出现 Invalid key length，请你确定是否开启了此功能，并且 key 的长度是否为 64 位长度，且只有小写字母和数字。"},"497":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"page","content":"云函数","url":"/docs/usage/serverless"},"498":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless","content":"使用 MixSpace 的云函数功能"},"499":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#介绍","content":"介绍"},"500":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#使用","content":"使用"},"501":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#1-进入云函数设置界面","content":"1. 进入云函数设置界面"},"502":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#2-下载扩展包","content":"2. 下载扩展包"},"503":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#3-导入","content":"3. 导入"},"504":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#开发者文档","content":"开发者文档"},"505":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#介绍","content":"云函数是 Mix Space 中的一个重要功能，它极大地提升了使用者在 Mix Space 中的体验。通过云函数，Mix Space 可以额外实现实现歌单解析，追番列表等等的功能。"},"506":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#介绍","content":"你可以在此处看到 Mix Space 目前收录的云函数 Snappets"},"507":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#使用","content":"有一些前端主题需要使用云函数，这个时候你需要进入到云函数设置界面，将云函数代码填入到对应的位置。"},"508":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#1-进入云函数设置界面","content":"进入后台管理，点击左侧菜单栏的 其他 - 云函数，即可进入云函数管理页面。"},"509":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#2-下载扩展包","content":"在右上方，点击 下载拓展包，你将会看到一个弹窗。"},"510":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-12","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#3-导入","content":"请在弹窗内请找到对应的主题的云函数代码，点击导入，即可完成下载对应的云函数代码。"},"511":{"id":"/docs/usage/serverless-13","page_id":"/docs/usage/serverless","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/serverless#3-导入","content":"接下来，你可以在云函数管理页面看到你刚刚导入的云函数代码。"},"512":{"id":"/docs/usage/update","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"page","content":"更新 Mix Space","url":"/docs/usage/update"},"513":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update","content":"更新你的 MixSpace"},"514":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/update#core后端更新","content":"Core（后端）更新"},"515":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/update#docker-部署","content":"Docker 部署"},"516":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/update#进阶部署","content":"进阶部署"},"517":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/update#前端更新","content":"前端更新"},"518":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update","content":"开头介绍就说过，Mx-Space 分为前端和后端两个部分，因此，更新的时候二者也需要分开更新。"},"519":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update#core后端更新","content":"根据部署方式的不同，更新方式也有不同。"},"520":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update#docker-部署","content":"进入 core 所在文件夹，然后 docker compose pull && docker compose up -d"},"521":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update#进阶部署","content":"进入克隆 core 的文件夹，执行 git pull origin master 拉取新版本源码，随后正常进行 pnpm i -> pnpm build -> pnpm bundle。"},"522":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update#进阶部署","content":"随后 进入 ./apps/core/out，执行以下命令启动服务 pm2 start ecosystem.config.js"},"523":{"id":"/docs/usage/update-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/update","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/update#前端更新","content":"请根据自己所部署的主题跳转到对应的更新部分完成更新。"},"524":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"page","content":"xLog 集成","url":"/docs/usage/xlog"},"525":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-0","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog","content":"使用 xLog 集成"},"526":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-1","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#介绍","content":"介绍"},"527":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-2","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"heading","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#使用","content":"使用"},"528":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-3","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#介绍","content":"此功能需要："},"529":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-4","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#介绍","content":"Core: >=3.43.1"},"530":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-5","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#介绍","content":"xLog 功能可以将你的博客同步到 xLog 平台。"},"531":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-6","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#介绍","content":"具体就是 此文章已经由它的创作者签名并安全地存储在区块链上。"},"532":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-7","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#介绍","content":"当你没有为文章写摘要的时候，可以使用 xLog 平台生成的摘要，当然你也可以使用自己的 GPT API Key 去调用 GPT 去生成摘要。"},"533":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-8","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#使用","content":"在 系统 - 第三方服务集成，填写 xLog SiteId 即可，然后去 xLog 平台去升级为钱包登录即可。钱包的注册方法请根据 xLog 的引导一步步注册。"},"534":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-9","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#使用","content":"SiteId 是一个字符串，可以在 xLog 平台的设置 - 域名找到；例如 example.xlog.app，即 SiteId = example。"},"535":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-10","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#使用","content":"当你完成钱包的注册，并使用钱包登录 xLog 平台的时候，就完成设置工作了。"},"536":{"id":"/docs/usage/xlog-11","page_id":"/docs/usage/xlog","type":"text","url":"/docs/usage/xlog#使用","content":"接下来你发布文章的时候，会自动的进行同步和签名；当然，需要经过你的同意。"},"537":{"id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config","page_id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config","type":"page","content":"配置","url":"/docs/themes/shiro/config"},"538":{"id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config-0","page_id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config","type":"text","url":"/docs/themes/shiro/config","content":"Shiro 主题的配置文件信息"},"539":{"id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config-1","page_id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/shiro/config#配置项","content":"配置项"},"540":{"id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config-2","page_id":"/docs/themes/shiro/config","type":"heading","url":"/docs/themes/shiro/config#页脚信息-footer","content":"页脚信息 (footer)"},"541":{"id":"/docs/themes/